    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a sorcerer, you gain the following class features.</p><h3>Hit Points</h3><p><strong>Hit Dice:</strong> 1d6 per sorcerer level<br /><strong>Hit Points at 1st Level:</strong> 6 + your Constitution modifier<br /><strong>Hit Points at Higher Levels:</strong> 1d6 (or 4) + your Constitution modifier per sorcerer level after 1st</p><h3>Proficiencies</h3><p><strong>Armor:</strong> None<br /><strong>Weapons:</strong> Daggers, darts, light crossbows, quarterstaffs, sickle, slings<br /><strong>Tools:</strong> None<br /><strong>Saving Throws:</strong> Constitution, Charisma<br /><strong>Skills:</strong> Choose two from Arcana, Deception, Insight, Intimidation, Persuasion, and Religion</p><h1>Sorcerer Advancement</h1><table><thead><tr><th rowspan=\"2\">Level</th><th rowspan=\"2\">Proficiency Bonus</th><th rowspan=\"2\">Sorcery Points</th><th rowspan=\"2\">Features</th><th rowspan=\"2\">Cantrips Known</th><th colspan=\"9\">— Spell Slots Per Spell Level —</th></tr><tr><th>1st</th><th>2nd</th><th>3rd</th><th>4th</th><th>5th</th><th>6th</th><th>7th</th><th>8th</th><th>9th</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1st</td><td>+2</td><td>—</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.0bHsvDfOoAXZOxC2]{Spellcasting}, @UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.k8rkrATndDLDvxmc]{Eschew Materials}, @UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.dNIRhfa593zGn7H7]{Sorcerous Origin}</td><td>4</td><td>2</td><td>—</td><td>—</td><td>—</td><td>—</td><td>—</td><td>—</td><td>—</td><td>—</td></tr><tr><td>2nd</td><td>+2</td><td>2</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.wv3ZvDFeg34rJ4co]{Font of Magic}</td><td>4</td><td>3</td><td>—</td><td>—</td><td>—</td><td>—</td><td>—</td><td>—</td><td>—</td><td>—</td></tr><tr><td>3rd</td><td>+2</td><td>3</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.voY3QNCIaxVkAK50]{Metamagic} (@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.