l6g]{Aberrant Mind}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.59brkwcClVnKugvN]{Clockwork Soul}</p><p>Divine Soul</p><ul><li>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.frM3SPo6WgMcCQwR]{Arcana Domain}</li><li>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.l6FZis2eOVgKrSbF]{Death Domain}</li><li>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.OCBuUSvfPzzolSxD]{Forge Domain}</li><li>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.59Ovm4AM6RDULX7W]{Grave Domain}</li><li>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.BG3WfYwkNda5ra1v]{Knowledge Domain}</li><li>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.7p0W298gbsORqpKH]{Life Domain}</li><li>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.35ps69dvppuMt3Vw]{Light Domain}</li><li>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.qerBvwEJ9bZjrwD8]{Nature Domain}</li><li>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.zDQey2cG53dJkSuE]{Order Domain}</li><li>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.OHkjdfybP2wmEirb]{Peace Domain}</li><li>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.y1gAbzXrW3aezpXu]{Tempest Domain}</li><li>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.wXa5E9lLAELflBIE]{Trickery Domain}</li><li>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.7JZeoWbRAnR5j8fz]{Twilight Domain}</li><li>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.MY3acRXMeKb8cYVy]{War Domain}</li></ul><p>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.n4den7iEyl8YfxlF]{Draconic Bloodline}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.sRPMMppq3368BWjI]{Shadow Magic}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.YTOB4tTSOoiICdyD]{Storm Sorcery}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.SnkcV2oL1squtDur]{Wild Magic}</p><h1>Multiclassing</h1><p>Should you wish to mulitclass into the sorcerer, the prerequisites and proficiencies gained are listed below.</p><blockquote><h3>Sorcerer Multiclassing Prerequisites</h3><p><strong>Ability Score Minimum:</strong> As a multiclass character, you must have at least a Charisma score of 13 to take a level in this class, or to take a level in another class if you are already a sorcerer.</p></blockquote><blockquote><h3>Sorcerer Multiclassing Spell Slots</h3><p><strong>Spell Slots</strong> Add your levels in the sorcerer class to the appropriate levels from other classes to determine your available spell slots.</p></blockquote><p></p>",
